This map is based around an arabian highway.  I originally got the idea off a scene in the movie "JarHead" and decided to replicate it here.  Basically this is a highway with lots of abandoned cars and vehicles.  

The map supports up to 64 players but is recommended for 32 and below.  The map does have fog in it but don't worry it won't cause you any fps lag.  If anything it'll help with fps.  There are 2 bomb sites.  1 int he middle of the map and 1 across the highway from CT Spawn.  

Have fun and good luck!



I appreciate all feedback!

INTRODUCTION: A Green Party has come to power and prohibited consumption of meat. While all the vegetarians are happy, much of the population continues to purchase contraband meat at high prices.

COUNTER-TERRORISTS: Recently our intelligence has discovered a meat distribution plant in our country. The criminals operating it are expecting us and will try to cover up the evidence by planting a C4 explosive either by the meat storage room, or in their office building. Stop them!

TERRORISTS: The government has sent a militia force to stop us from feeding our country. But they will not have enough evidence against us if we destroy the meat in the storage or the money from the sales in the office. Plant a C4 at one of the sites and make sure that the charge goes off!

[THIS IS A CSGO PORT FOR CSS]

Intended for competitive and casual defusal mode.

  Terrorists are trying to destroy the antique and valuable ruins of a lost civilization somewhere in central / south America, Seal team 6 has been deployed to stop them. 

Includes two bomb sites.
Includes a  proper Mini-map (Ported panorama mini-map)
Includes Nav_mesh
Fully textured and clipped
Removes a lot of trees on low video settings (To support ancient potato machines)

This port does not include all features from its CSGO counterpart, due to CSS limitations. Therefore, some features and graphical changes have been made/removed. 

Changes in this port:
No dynamic lighting
Removed some CSGO detail props due to unfix-able lighting glitches regarding the models.
Not so perfect map lighting, due to engine not allowing me to push it more.
Less props.

About the lighting:

I did my best to make it so the overall level lighting looks similar to its CSGO counterpart, but alas i cannot make it any better than this. I also recompiled every single texture in the map with proper .vtf versions. Can be played in CSGO, although i do NOT recommend it as the original is far superior.

Csgo counterpart can be found here: https://gamebanana.com/maps/206072 or https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1809308995

This map is a mirrored map with small changes to each side (props, decals, etc..). It is based in a market square and surrounding area. There are 2 main routes to each bomb site, A and B. A is faster to get to, but harder to hold off. B takes longer to get to and is more risky, but when you get there it is easier to hold off.

There are 4 market stalls, each of which you can use cover for. There is also a storage unit to the side which could be used for an alternate route. To get to B, you must cross a wide open space which is dangerous because of long-range fire.

The map is designed more to be like an FY or an AIM map, but it has bomb sites because it is larger. Instead of the bomb sites being the primary objective, they are more of a secondary objective for stalemates and whatnot.

I hope you enjoy the map, and thanks for downloading.
